#text=The other day I decided to bake a cake so I got out some flour , eggs , sugar , and frosting .
#text=Once I mixed all of the ingredients together I put them in a pan and into an oven and set the oven to 400 degrees .
#text=I put the cake into the oven and set the cooking alarm for 12 minutes .
#text=Once the cake was fully cooked and the cooking alarm rang I took the cake out of the oven and let it cool off for a couple of minutes .

#text=After those couple of minutes were up I took some frosting after taking the cake out of the cooking pan and onto a plate , which just happened to be chocolate , and spread it over the cake lightly with a butter knife .
#text=Once I had completely covered the cake in frosting I put it gently into a box and put it into the fridge until I wanted to eat it .
#text=Once I ate it tasted really very good . ''
